 me and I try to support them.\", \"from\": 1552, \"to\": 1607, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"All athletes\", \"from\": 1553, \"to\": 1565}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Steven and Matthew [Immers] are also part of that.'\", \"from\": 1608, \"to\": 1659, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Immers\", \"from\": 1628, \"to\": 1634}, {\"ngram\": \"part\", \"from\": 1645, \"to\": 1649}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Asked how Van de Velde has coped with the increased levels of scrutiny ahead of the Paris Olympics, Van den Hoogenband added: 'I think he reacts well and level-headedly.\", \"from\": 1661, \"to\": 1830, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Van de Velde\", \"from\": 1671, \"to\": 1683}, {\"ngram\": \"the increased levels\", \"from\": 1699, \"to\": 1719}, {\"ngram\": \"scrutiny\", \"from\": 1723, \"to\": 1731}, {\"ngram\": \"the Paris Olympics\", \"from\": 1741, \"to\": 1759}, {\"ngram\": \"Van den Hoogenband\", \"from\": 1761, \"to\": 1779}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'He's not going to downplay it.\", \"from\": 1832, \"to\": 1863, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"We have to respect it and help him as a member of the team, to be able to perform.\", \"from\": 1864, \"to\": 1946, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a member\", \"from\": 1902, \"to\": 1910}, {\"ngram\": \"the team\", \"from\": 1914, \"to\": 1922}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'I think he is doing well.\", \"from\": 1948, \"to\": 1974, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"With respect for all the feelings of other people.\", \"from\": 1975, \"to\": 2025, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"respect\", \"from\": 1980, \"to\": 1987}, {\"ngram\": \"all the feelings\", \"from\": 1992, \"to\": 2008}, {\"ngram\": \"other people\", \"from\": 2012, \"to\": 2024}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I think he has a good focus, with his partner, because they have to do it together.\", \"from\": 2026, \"to\": 2109, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a good focus\", \"from\": 2041, \"to\": 2053}, {\"ngram\": \"his partner\", \"from\": 2060, \"to\": 2071}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Hopefully we can soon talk about the sport again.'\", \"from\": 2110, \"to\": 2160, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the sport\", \"from\": 2143, \"to\": 2152}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Van de Velde's team-mate Matthew Immers has also defended his fellow volleyball player, describing him as 'like a second father'.\", \"from\": 2162, \"to\": 2291, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Van de Velde's team-mate Matthew Immers\", \"from\": 2162, \"to\": 2201}, {\"ngram\": \"his fellow volleyball player\", \"from\": 2220, \"to\": 2248}, {\"ngram\": \"a second father\", \"from\": 2274, \"to\": 2289}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'It's a shame that people talk about him like that,' the 23-year-old said.\", \"from\": 2293, \"to\": 2367, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a shame\", \"from\": 2299, \"to\": 2306}, {\"ngram\": \"people\", \"from\": 2312, \"to\": 2318}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'I know the Steven of today, and I am happy about that.\", \"from\": 2368, \"to\": 2423, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the Steven\", \"from\": 2376, \"to\": 2386}, {\"ngram\": \"today\", \"from\": 2390, \"to\": 2395}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'He's a very good partner for me.\", \"from\": 2425, \"to\": 2458, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a very good partner\", \"from\": 2431, \"to\": 2450}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We have fun and good company on and off the field, that's the most important thing for me.\", \"from\": 2459, \"to\": 2549, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"fun and good company\", \"from\": 2467, \"to\": 2487}, {\"ngram\": \"the field\", \"from\": 2499, \"to\": 2508}, {\"ngram\": \"the most important thing\", \"from\": 2517, \"to\": 2541}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'I feel comfortable with him, we take good care of each other.\", \"from\": 2551, \"to\": 2613, \